# Build context is the repo root (.do/app.yaml source_dir: /), so these
# globs are matched against the whole monorepo. Keep host-built artifacts and
# secrets out of the image: node_modules is reinstalled fresh for Linux inside
# the build, and committing the host's (Windows) native binaries would break it.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/playwright-report
**/test-results
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.log
.git
.github
.vscode
.idea
